ViridianCity_Text_CanCarryMonsAnywhere::
    .string "Those BALLS at your waist!\n"
    .string "You have BRAINROTS, do you not?\p"
    .string "In SAFE ZONES, registered\n"
    .string "partners are allowed.$"

